high_descs: Stand in front of bed, turn left then turn right, face the desk.
Now turn right towards bed
Pick up pen, carry it
Place pen inside the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with pen on it
Now carry bowl towards the desk.
Place bowl with pen onto desk.
anns.task_desc: Go pick up pen, place it onto bowl, then put bowl on top of desk.

high_descs: Turn left towards the door and then turn right towards the desk.
Pick up the pen from the desk.
Turn right, walk towards the edge of the desk, and then turn left to face the desk.
Place the pen the the bowl to the right of the book on the desk.
Pick up the bowl with the pen.
Turn left and walk towards the other side of the desk and then turn right to face it.
Place the bowl to the right of the stack of books closest to the wall.
anns.task_desc: Place the bowl with a pen on the desk.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the white door, and then turn right and walk to the wooden desk next to the bed.
Pick up the left pen on the desk.
Walk to the right side of the desk.
Place the pen in the glass bowl on the desk that is closest to the waste bin.
Pick up the glass bowl on the desk closest to the waste bin.
Walk to the left side of the wooden desk.
Place the glass bowl with the pen in it on the top shelf of the wooden desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass bowl with a pen in it on top of the top shelf of the wooden desk.
